{"tid":184371,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷疑中病毒] 大部份檔案損毀 ,無法開啟","createTime":"2017-04-02T17:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T04:04:20.000Z","uid":72431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47a8837818844bedbbe8ddc4101c6c2f5bd85434","tid":184371,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:46:55.000Z","msg":"BACKGROUND:<br />\n首先小弟有日突然間入唔到WINDOW USER AC <br />\n入左去一個TEMP USER AC(版面類似 安全模式咁, 桌面黑色、咩都無)<br />\n之後上面查 話係WINDOW CONNECT唔到 我個WINDOW USER AC( E.G. ABC.USER)<br />\n咁我之後跟番D 教學整兩整, 入番我個AC ,不過個DESKTOP無哂野, CHROME BOOKMARK咩都無哂, &quot;我的文件&quot;200個檔得番30個檔,(唔見左個D檔揾唔到) ,咁我再之後用WINDOW 個WINDOW RECOVERY ,番去上星期個還原點,試左兩次,還原失敗,就無再做野,拎去比人整<br />\n<br />\n整機佬嘗試做DATA RECOVERY ,再重裝WINDOWS ,話可以將一D刪左既檔案復原,之後佢係揾到D刪左既檔,同以前個FILE DIRECTORY , 以:/DESKTOP為例, 以前DESKTOP D檔都係到, 不過就開唔到,佢都話無辦法開到。<br />\n<br />\n損壞的檔案包括: WORD ,EXCEL , JPG ,MP3 ,咩類形都開唔到, 不過睇番FILE SIZE 係足既, 例如WORD 有4 MB<br />\n<br />\n以EXCEL 為例:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7w0HpOS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7w0HpOS.png&h=75d65bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我嘗試以 DataNumen Word Repair 去修復 WORD 檔, <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/057ahFj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F057ahFj.png&h=46dbb247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢以似話我個FILE EXTENSION 係XML , 不過我睇明明係DOCX <br />\n<br />\n我個CASE最奇怪位係部份檔案(20%) 無問題 , 80%檔案改左路俓(例如DESKTOP 咩都無哂, 揾唔番個檔) ,而且損毀(開唔到)<br />\n<br />\n以我推斷,一係之前WINDOW UPDATE 失敗(不過係發生問題前一星期既事,而且即刻無事), 或者係中病毒, 不過我果排無特別DOWN 野。 <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打,可以幫我開番D 檔   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fa19acfa1a0b29c679b68e60415a4fbd252d2e","tid":184371,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"巴打唔明我打咩 ,<br />\n我再解釋番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b2d174ba272797fb29a490dd224edc07b63ee7","tid":184371,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"Docx 的確應用左 xml"},{"pid":"0decb1987c6f375cac227dcf6e1933f7ebe86518","tid":184371,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Docx 的確應用左 xml</blockquote><br />\n你指咩DOCX本身都有XML?"},{"pid":"3be7634332a7ae5da9d82974710f1441ca074889","tid":184371,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:33:45.000Z","msg":"所以話一買部機返屋企就馬上去set 永久不更新 <br />\n以前一更完個window實有古怪野或者唔兼容搞到d軟件自己打自己 成部機廢埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e9e03cc3998445f60423ce309e012de03aefa7","tid":184371,"uid":99960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"洗機重裝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de30d5f027aa69f3bc053dd188878c8cd39d519","tid":184371,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"整linux 手指救返d file再重裝os"},{"pid":"c2670d7ef5c59b4f4de95ce6e0167a331f62ee67","tid":184371,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以話一買部機返屋企就馬上去set 永久不更新 <br />\n以前一更完個window實有古怪野或者唔兼容搞到d軟件自己打自己 成部機廢埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對d識電腦既人黎講，裝linux好過。新手搞完一大輪年年唔係中毒就係壞windows，最後都係要洗機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fab32d19561c3ac1e4c6795a4e523140803579","tid":184371,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"其實我機已洗 只係想開番damaged docs"}]}